<h1>Create scientist</h1>

Will create a new scientist with provided parameters. <br>
If any parameter is missing, will use default value <br>
instead and create a record anyway. It can be edited <br>
later <br>


<%= form_for @scientist, url: { action: "create" }  do |f| %>
  <p>
    <%= f.label :madness %><br>
    <%= f.text_field :madness %>
  </p>
 
  <p>
    <%= f.label :attempts %><br>
    <%= f.text_field :attempts %>
  </p>
 
  <p>
    <%= f.submit "Create scientist" %>
  </p>
<% end %>
